5FE9 1A10             (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00068                SEI                   THEN SET
5FEB FDCA06           (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00069                STD    HORIZ
5FEE 3121             (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00070                LEAY   1,Y            NOW POINT AT DATA
