6004 B7CA00           (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00079         PR3502 STA    CONTRL
6007 3521             (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00080                PULS   CC,Y           RESTORE INTERRUPT THE WAY WE WERE!
6009 A6A4             (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00081                LDA    ,Y            GET WIDTH BACK
600B 4C               (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00082                INCA                  ADD THE SPACE
600C 5F               (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00083                CLRB
600D 44               (sm/src/RRTEXT.ASM):00084                LSRA                  BACK TO BYTES
